In an interview with OAP Toolz on the Beat FM, Big Brother finalists; Alex, Cee C, Miracle, Nina and Tobi discuss their relationships with fellow housemates, how they feel about the game and more. While Nina addresses her current relationship status with her boyfriend, Collins, Alex calls her out on giving her negative vibes. Watch
